    "body": "Either:\n1) check the symlink into git\n2) move the files into node_modules\n3) use a script to create the symlinks\n\nHaving a paths configuration api seems like excessive configuration. The goal of browserify is to bring node's module system to the browser because it is nice and you can reuse lots of your code between node and the browser. node does just fine without a paths configuration so browserify doesn't need it either.\n",
